ola (0.10.3.nojsmin-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Drop all minified javascript, and repackage as a 'nojsmin' tarball.
    Don't call it .dfsg.tar.gz, because it has *nothing* to do with any
    reasonable interpretation of the DFSG, only with some armchair
    lawyering. Closes: #760414.
  * debian/ola.links: add symlinks to packaged versions of used
    javascript libraries
  * debian/control: add dependencies to packages containing the above
  * debian/rules: remove override_dh_install target, which is now
    obsoleted by the above.
  * debian/control: add dependencies on lsb-base for packages requiring it,
    silencing lintian

